03:10.148 --> 03:11.941
And I don't even have
the guts to go see him.

03:12.025 --> 03:14.736
- Jesus had
a pretty powerful papa too.

03:14.819 --> 03:18.865
Many people said he'd never be
as dope as his father.

03:18.948 --> 03:21.409
