04:08.623 --> 04:09.958
- But they will not triumph.

04:10.041 --> 04:11.292
- No.
- No.

04:11.376 --> 04:12.877
Because Eli is strong.

04:12.961 --> 04:15.630
And our family is strong.

04:15.713 --> 04:19.676
And the love and support
of this incredible congregation

04:19.759 --> 04:20.718
is strong.

04:20.802 --> 04:21.844
all: [scattered]
Amen.

04:21.928 --> 04:23.638
- You know,
Amber and I are very proud...

04:23.721 --> 04:24.681
- We are.

04:24.764 --> 04:27.517
- To be the people
that everyone is turning to

04:27.600 --> 04:28.726
in this moment of need.

04:28.810 --> 04:29.727
- Your leaders. We are here.

04:29.811 --> 04:31.062
- Yes.
- For you.

04:31.145 --> 04:32.981
- We're--we're ready
to be front and center

04:33.064 --> 04:34.816
as the leaderships
of the church.

04:34.899 --> 04:39.404
- I have made a hashtag.
#EliGemsHome.

04:39.487 --> 04:40.989
'Cause we all want Eli
to come on home.

04:41.072 --> 04:41.948
- Yeah, we do.

04:42.031 --> 04:43.324
