a little bit like stone,

04:43.408 --> 04:45.034
so instead of Gemstone,
it's "GemsHome."

04:45.118 --> 04:47.829
It's #EliGemsHome.

04:47.912 --> 04:49.414
Let's go viral with that.

04:49.497 --> 04:51.791
- You do it so--so any photos
you take today

04:51.874 --> 04:53.668
or if you're just thinking
about my daddy,

04:53.751 --> 04:55.378
you just tag it GemsHomes.

04:55.461 --> 04:57.088
- Eli. EliGemsHomes.
- Eli--

04:57.171 --> 04:58.548
- #Eli...
- #EliGemsHomes.

04:58.631 --> 05:00.717
- Gems--GemsHome.
- GemsHome.

05:00.800 --> 05:02.552
