he was bound to snap

10:11.068 --> 10:14.572
and do what he did
regardless of anything we did.

10:14.655 --> 10:17.783
So we did not instigate
anything, all right?

10:17.867 --> 10:19.452
- It seems like we did, though.

10:19.535 --> 10:22.371
- Well, I don't think it does
seem like that, Chad, okay?

10:22.455 --> 10:24.373
