a damn power play with me.

10:24.457 --> 10:27.043
- I'm not--look, I'm not trying
to do a power plays.

10:27.126 --> 10:28.210
- Well,
you're doing power plays.

10:28.294 --> 10:29.754
- He's genuinely concerned,
Jesse.

10:29.837 --> 10:30.838
