10:30.921 --> 10:32.381
- Levi,
when I want your opinion,

10:32.465 --> 10:34.175
I will hit your fucking face
with a wet towel.

10:34.258 --> 10:35.217
Do you understand me?

10:36.635 --> 10:38.888
- So what?
