my scientists,

11:48.874 --> 11:50.960
all the people in my lab,
my developers,

11:51.043 --> 11:53.462
the lab rats, it's a wash.

11:53.546 --> 11:55.881
Well, why you do it then,
Baby Billy?

11:55.965 --> 11:57.800
'Cause I'm selfless.

11:57.883 --> 11:59.718
And I want to heal
as many people

11:59.802 --> 12:01.429
