more clear.

12:55.399 --> 12:57.067
I'm doing all this
for you and baby Lionel.

12:57.151 --> 12:59.987
That's why I'm selling
these here...

13:00.070 --> 13:02.031
health elixirs.

13:02.114 --> 13:04.867
- Didn't you hear
my daddy got shot?

13:04.950 --> 13:06.368
- Yes, I did.

13:06.452 --> 13:07.828
And I'm praying for him.

13:07.912 --> 13:10.331
- Baby Billy, you ran out
on me and baby Lionel

13:10.414 --> 13:12.291
just like you did
your other son.

13:12.374 --> 13:14.502
[somber music]

13:14.585 --> 13:15.544
- What did you say?

13:15.628 --> 13:17.254
- I know about Harmon.

13:17.338 --> 13:19.882
How come you didn't
never tell me about him?

13:21.800 --> 13:23.469
- You two little pigs squeal?

13:23.552 --> 13:25.221
- She deserved to know.

13:25.304 --> 13:27.890
She needs to move on,
and she needs to move out

13:27.973 --> 13:29.892
of my house.

13:29.975 --> 13:31.852
- Get over her. I'm gonna spank
the shit out of both of you.

13:31.936 --> 13:32.895
- No.
- I'ma get you. I'ma get you.

13:32.978 --> 13:34.271
- No. What? Ah!
- Yeah. On my knee.

13:34.355 --> 13:35.523
Get down here.
- Ow! Ow!

13:35.606 --> 13:36.524
- Bad boy!
- Ah! Ah! Ah!

13:36.607 --> 13:37.858
- He's so bad.

13:37.942 --> 13:39.109
Little weak boy.

13:39.193 --> 13:40.236
Get down. Get down.

13:40.319 --> 13:42.238
- [yelps]
- To hell with all of you!

13:42.321 --> 13:44.031
All the money
I'm making out here,

13:44.114 --> 13:45.783
trying to provide
for my family,

13:45.866 --> 13:48.202
and you're gonna question
